"By tapping the button, you agree to the Terms of Service and Privacy Policy. The device activation information and location will be sent to HMD Global.

Auto Software Update notification, which installs the latest updates for you, will also be enabled. This may use up a small portion of your data budget. The services will access the Internet whenever they need to.

You will be charged for these services if they exceed your current data plan when they access mobile networks."

"By tapping the button, you agree to the Terms of Service. Your data will be processed according to HMD’s Privacy Policy. The device activation information with one-time device location will be sent to HMD Global. Mobile data charges may apply."

"Join the Nokia User Experience program. Learn more. "

Your participation in the user experience program helps HMD Global to better understand what you like about your Nokia device, and what you think needs to be improved. From time to time, we may receive anonymous data with technical characteristics about your device, such as a file containing data about a software crash that may have happened. Please note that such data will not be transmitted over a mobile data connection. We love hearing what you think about your Nokia device!
